{"tid":840634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買魚放湖扮豐收　習笑騎騎受騙","createTime":"2018-09-29T03:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T02:17:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":286,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"cb76a7561fabdabf17883290d4343d79e76e62d8","tid":840634,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:10:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180929/20510766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510766&d=xH5%2FwXp60YWt8vnw4YjGDtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=aed14f4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510766&h=902648a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180929/20510766</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月29日 <br />\n<br />\n買魚放湖扮豐收　習笑騎騎受騙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180929/large/29cf05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F29cf05p.jpg&h=5c5d8d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習看到魚穫笑開顏，殊不知是幹部造假。新華社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】內地弄虛作假，似乎從沒改變！習前日到吉林松原市查干湖考察。有網友翻牆在Twitter爆料指，松原市全城封路，警察站崗好幾天。當地幹部為了「展示」查干湖豐富漁穫，竟從其他地方買來大批魚放進湖中，而且彩排了好幾天。<br />\n<br />\n根據內地官方媒體報道，習近平當日從黑龍江齊齊哈爾趕赴吉林松原市，到查干湖了解當地生態保育情況。報道形容，習同漁場職工們親切交談。央視更發佈當日的新聞片段，可見查干湖的漁民收穫豐厚，條條魚都相當肥大。習見狀大喜，眉開眼笑，祝願大家「年年有魚，年年有餘」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有網友在Twitter卻踢爆，這一段都是假象，「昨天來松原查干湖，全城封路，警察站崗好幾天，查干湖現買的魚撒湖裏，而且綵排了好幾天」。在蒙古語中被稱為「白色的湖」或「聖潔的湖」的查干湖，是東北平原上最大的淡水湖，水產極為豐富，同時也是候鳥的主要棲息地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塑造成「麥田守望者」<br />\n<br />\n另外，習近平曾到黑龍江農墾建三江管理局，了解糧食生產和收穫情況。當地幹部特別為習開出一條路，讓他走進麥田拍攝宣傳照，將他塑造成「麥田守望者」。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n廣東出口大跌　華放眼新興巿場<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n毛澤東建國真言變禍國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n振興20年　東北依然一蹶不振<br />\n<br />\n廣東出口大跌　華放眼新興巿場<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東建國真言變禍國<br />\n<br />\n北巡糧倉　對內安撫對外表態　習不惜鎖國　與美鬥到底"},{"pid":"58bad6e5774aa52fcafb5337e6cd3b28e22946e6","tid":840634,"uid":50663,"like":329,"dislike":1,"score":328,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"稱號get 麥田守望者 亡國屬性+10"},{"pid":"198940dcaac2418f9bffca395e2356f4a1381e3a","tid":840634,"uid":118120,"like":255,"dislike":3,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"同毛澤民視察農田收成一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5ccff90f48914db3ca0c9f0fbaef1ef0e16a8c","tid":840634,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10aec8a6caf45624a25a6552b764fb451dc1c10d","tid":840634,"uid":52595,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37d453be1f74c94a175a05e7ea7af5e28241f371","tid":840634,"uid":108467,"like":307,"dislike":3,"score":304,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/113652_6d90cdf82a4e59811c58120d00c08c1f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F113652_6d90cdf82a4e59811c58120d00c08c1f.gif&h=2c0aabc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ea648c0b9af44ae77982313c84db7befd01c26c","tid":840634,"uid":15309,"like":143,"dislike":5,"score":138,"quote":{"pid":"37d453be1f74c94a175a05e7ea7af5e28241f371","tid":840634,"uid":108467,"like":307,"dislike":3,"score":304,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/113652_6d90cdf82a4e59811c58120d00c08c1f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F113652_6d90cdf82a4e59811c58120d00c08c1f.gif&h=2c0aabc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:40:09.000Z","